We are so excited to begin the new school year in only a few short weeks! As we prepare for the new year, we are needing to collect Chromebooks from students in order to sanitize and update software to ensure all technology is ready for use on the first day of school (Wednesday, September 9th -remotely).

If you have not turned in your Ipad/Chromebook device, you have until Monday, August 24, 2020, to do so. Students in grades 2 & 3 may return their devices (iPads) to their home school. Students in grades 6 & 9 are asked to turn their devices in at their (assigned middle/high school). If you have additional questions, please contact your child's building principal. #WeAreTPS
